i\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Pangasinan language|Pangasinan]]\n| sakey\n| dua, duara\n| talo, talora\n| apat, apatira\n| too\n| abong\n| aso\n| niyog\n| ageo\n| balo\n| sikatayo\n| anto\n| pool\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Ilocano language|Ilocano]]\n| maysa\n| dua\n| tallo\n| uppat\n| tao\n| balay\n| aso\n| niog\n| aldaw\n| baro\n| datayo\n| ania\n| apoy\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Ivatan language|Ivatan]]\n| asa\n| dadowa\n| tatdo\n| apat\n| tao\n| vahay\n| chito\n| niyoy\n| araw\n| va-yo\n| yaten\n| ango\n| apoy\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Ibanag language|Ibanag]]\n| tadday\n| dua\n| tallu\n| appa'\n| tolay\n| balay\n| kitu\n| niuk\n| aggaw\n| bagu\n| sittam\n| anni\n| afi\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Yogad language|Yogad]]\n| tata\n| addu\n| tallu\n| appat\n| tolay\n| binalay\n| atu\n| iyyog\n| agaw\n| bagu\n| sikitam\n| gani\n| afuy\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Gaddang language|Gaddang]]\n| antet\n| addwa\n| tallo\n| appat\n| tolay\n| balay\n| atu\n| ayog\n| aw\n| bawu\n| ikkanetam\n| sanenay\n| afuy\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Tboli language|Tboli]]\n| sotu\n| lewu\n| tlu\n| fat\n| tau\n| gunu\n| ohu\n| lefo\n| kdaw\n| lomi\n| tekuy\n| tedu\n| ofih\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Kadazan language|Kadazan]]\n| iso\n| duvo\n| tohu\n| apat\n| tuhun\n| hamin\n| tasu\n| piasau\n| tadau\n| vagu\n| tokou\n| onu\n| tapui\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Malay language|Malay]]/'''[[Indonesian language|Indonesian]]'''\n| satu\n| dua\n| tiga\n| empat\n| orang\n| rumah\n| anjing\n| kelapa/nyiur\n| hari\n| baru/baharu\n| kita\n| apa\n| api\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Javanese language|Javanese]]\n| siji\n| loro\n| telu\n| papat\n| uwong\n| omah\n| asu\n| klapa/kambil\n| hari\n| anyar/enggal\n| kita\n| apa/anu\n| geni\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Acehnese language|Acehnese]]\n| sa\n| duwa\n| lh\u00e8\u00eb\n| peu\u00ebt\n| ureu\u00ebng\n| rumoh/bal\u00e8\u00eb\n| as\u00e8\u00eb\n| u\n| uro\u00eb\n| bar\u00f4\n| (geu)tanyo\u00eb\n| peu\u00eb\n| apuy\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Lampung language|Lampung]]\n| sai\n| khua\n| 